1.0.name: wordpress/cloriato-lite
1.0.description: The Website built using Cloriato Theme is supereasy to build and is very simplistic in design, the visitors love to see the whole content clearly. Cloriato Theme got several theme options to allow changing and manipulating literally everything in the site. You would absolutely love to built your site using Cloriato Theme.
